DataElement.Name: LRN
LRN
LRN
DataElement.DescriptionLine: Unique reference number of the declaration.

DataElement.Name: Sanoman tunniste
Meddelandets identifiering
Message identification
DataElement.DescriptionLine: Identification of a single message. A five-character string assigned by Customs is followed by a reference number assigned by the message sender.

DataElement.Name: Tavaroiden arvioitu esittämispäivä ja -aika
Varonas uppskattade presentationsdatum och klockslag
Estimated presentation of goods date and time
Luvanhaltijan tunnistenumero
Tillståndshavarens
Holder of the authorisation identification no.
Luvan tyyppi
Tillståndets typ
Authorisation type
DataElement.DescriptionLine: Enter the type of authorisation that the holder is linked to (authorisation data is entered in data group 'Documents produced, certificates and authorisations, additional references').

DataGroup.Name: Edustaja
Ombud
Representative
DataGroup.DescriptionLine: If a representative is used by the declarant, enter representative's identity data.

DataElement.Name: Edustajan toimipaikkakoodi
Ombudets kontorskod
Representative office code
DataElement.DescriptionLine: Enter nationally allocated trader office code, if representative has one.

DataElement.Name: Ilmoittajan toimipaikkakoodi
Deklarantens kontorskod
Declarant office code
DataElement.DescriptionLine: Enter nationally allocated trader office code, if declarant has one.

DataGroup.Name: Esitetyt asiakirjat, todistukset ja luvat, lisäviitteet.
Framlagda dokument, certifikat och tillstånd, ytterligare referensuppgifter
Documents produced, certificates and authorisations, additional references

DataElement.Name: Viitenumero/UCR
Referensnummer/UCR
Reference number/UCR
DataElement.DescriptionLine: Enter a unique consignment reference UCR, if one has been assigned by the consignor. UCR remains the same throughout the supply chain. It can be WCO (ISO 15459) -code or an equivalent.

DataElement.Name: Kontin tunnistenumero
Containernummer
Container identification number
DataElement.DescriptionLine: Enter the number(s) of sea container or semitrailer identification number(s).

DataElement.Name: Lähetys-/vientimaan koodi
Kod för avsändnings-/exportland
Country of dispatch/export code
DataElement.DescriptionLine: Enter the original country code if dispatch. If there has been a stoppage unrelated to the transport of goods or a commercial transaction (e.g. sale or processing), indicate the last intermediate country. Consolidation of the goods en-route is not considered as a stoppage in this data element.

DataElement.Name: Määrämaan koodi
Kod för destinationsland
Country of destination code
DataElement.DescriptionLine: Enter country code FI if the goods remain in Finland. If the goods are to be transited to another EU country enter the code of that country.

DataElement.Name: Tuojan toimipaikkakoodi
Importörens kontorskod
Consignee office code
DataElement.DescriptionLine: Enter nationally allocated trader office code, if consignee has one.

DataElement.Name: Viitenumero/UCR
Referensnummer/UCR
Reference number/UCR
DataElement.DescriptionLine: Enter a unique consignment reference UCR, if one has been assigned by the consignor. UCR remains the same throughout the supply chain. It can be WCO (ISO 15459) -code or an equivalent.

DataElement.Name: Tavaran kuvaus
Varubeskrivning
Description of goods
DataElement.DescriptionLine: Enter the common trade name precise enough in order to identify and classify the goods. General terms e.g. “clothes” may not be used. The EU Commission maintains a list of unacceptable general terms.

DataElement.Name: Luokitustyyppi
Klassificeringstyp
Classification type
DataElement.DescriptionLine: Enter CUS code if the goods are subject to a TARIC measure in relation with a CUS code. CUS code applies to some chemical substances and preparations. Declaration of CUS code does not waive from the declaration of the description of goods.

DataElement.Name: Tavaran koodi – yhdistetyn nimikkeistön koodi
Varukod – KN-nummer
Commodity code - Combined Nomenclature code
DataElement.DescriptionLine: A minimum of 6 digits must be declared.

DataElement.Name: Bruttomassa
Bruttomassa
Gross mass
DataElement.DescriptionLine: Enter the gross mass in kilograms. The gross mass includes the goods and packaging, but not the means of transport or containers. If the gross mass is below 1 kilogram, enter the value with up to maximum of 6 decimal places, e.g. "0,654". If the gross mass exceeds 1 kg, you can enter the value rounded to the closest full kilogram.

DataElement.Name: Lisäpaljousyksiköt
Extra mängdenheter
Supplementary units
DataElement.DescriptionLine: When indicating a measurement required by Taric, no unit is declared.

DataElement.Name: Toimijan ilmoittama paljous, paljousyksikkö
Mängd som anges av aktören, mängdenhet
Measurement declared by trader, measurement unit
Lähetysmerkinnät
Märken
Shipping marks
DataElement.DescriptionLine: Enter a free-form description of the marks and numbers on transport units or packages. If the packages are not marked, enter "no markings". If the number of packages is 0, the marks and numbers shall be the same as on the goods item for which the total number of packages has been entered.

DataElement.Name: Kolliluku
Antal kollin
Number of packages
DataElement.DescriptionLine: Enter the number of packages. If there are goods from several goods items within the one and same package, enter the value "1" at least in one of the goods items, and value "0" in the other goods items.

DataGroup.Name: Esitetyt asiakirjat, todistukset ja luvat, lisäviitteet.
Framlagda dokument, certifikat och tillstånd, ytterligare referensuppgifter
Documents produced, certificates and authorisations, additional references
Yksinkertaistettu ilmoitus / Edeltävät asiakirjat
Förenklad deklaration / Tidigare dokument
Simplified declaration / Previous documents
DataGroup.DescriptionLine: Enter previous document. Most often entry summary declaration, summary declaration or T1-transit declaration is used. If the country of dispatch is Norway and there is no previous procedure, previous document is not declared. If previous declaration is submitted to Finnish Customs UTU system, enter MRN of that declaration.

DataElement.Name: Kontin tunnistenumero
Containernummer
Container identification number
DataElement.DescriptionLine: Enter the number(s) of sea container or semitrailer identification number(s).
